## Project structure

```
tests/
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ MyApp.Domain.Tests/          ŌåÉ entity and value object behaviour
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ MyApp.Application.Tests/     ŌåÉ handler, validator, pipeline behaviour
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ MyApp.Infrastructure.Tests/  ŌåÉ EF Core, HTTP clients, adapters
ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ MyApp.Api.Tests/             ŌåÉ full request/response via WebApplicationFactory
```

Each test project references only the layer it tests; it does not skip layers.

